<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="9" type="remarks">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="9">Remark.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="9">
Already 
<bibRefCitation author="Christoph, H" journalOrPublisher="Horae Societatis Entomologicae Rossicae" pageId="0" pageNumber="9" pagination="3 - 55" publicationUrl="https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/12777478" refId="B2" refString="Christoph, H, 1873. Weiterer Beitrag zum Verzeichnisse der in Nord-Persien einheimischen Schmetterlinge. Horae Societatis Entomologicae Rossicae 10 (3): 3 - 55, https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/12777478" title="Weiterer Beitrag zum Verzeichnisse der in Nord-Persien einheimischen Schmetterlinge." url="https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/12777478" volume="10" year="1873">Christoph (1873)</bibRefCitation>
reported this species from Golestan, from a specimen taken around oaks; its is therefore possible that he mistook a 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Ulmaceae" genus="Tischeria" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Tischeria" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="9" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="9">Tischeria</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species. Later 
<bibRefCitation author="Mirzayans, H" journalOrPublisher="Entomologie et Phytopathologie Appliquees" pageId="0" pageNumber="9" pagination="15 - 23" refId="B27" refString="Mirzayans, H, Kalali, G, 1970. Contribution a la connaissance de la faune des Lepidopteres de l'Iran (2). Entomologie et Phytopathologie Appliquees 29: 15 - 23" title="Contribution a la connaissance de la faune des Lepidopteres de l'Iran (2)." volume="29" year="1970">Mirzayans and Kalali (1970)</bibRefCitation>
recorded it from leafmines, and also our new records are based on the characteristic leafmines, as rearing failed, but confirmation by adults would still be required as several species feed on 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Rubus" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Rubus" order="Rosales" pageId="0" pageNumber="9" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="9">Rubus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
